TextSpam Use Cases

User enters message, frequency.
	Numbers should enter field correctly.

User enters number manually and adds the number to the sending list.
	On clicking add, the number should enter the sending list and be stored.

User sends the message in queue to the recipients on the sending list.
	message should send to all recipients the same amount of times.

User has sending list set and adds conversation.
	Conversation appears in new activity and is stored in database.
Tutorial w/ and w/o menu key.
 	should appear correctly for each one.
User sends message to multiple recipients.
	each recipient recieves same message same amount of times.

Switch between fragments.
	make sure they don't crash.

Send messges without body.
